data.description: Location, location! Wonderful property in quiet Sandy neighborhood! Come see this clean home featuring two spacious primary bedrooms, huge patio perfect for entertaining, and upgraded windows. This beautiful corner lot sits in a cozy cul-de-sac with minimal traffic. Newer upgraded 3-ton AC unit and furnace was installed in 2022. Basement features spacious bedroom with adjoining room that could be used as a den or entertainment area. Truly a must see!!!
